  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327850/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1764942945\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327850/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1764942945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327850/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1764942945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Gold Rush - is the simplest 2D game in which you have to overcome various traps and look for treasures.<br>The essence of this game is very simple. Your main task is to explore a variety of locations and find the right treasures. But don't think that everything will be very easy. On your way there will be a huge variety of traps that you will have to overcome. Think over your every step and every action and this game will definitely not make you bored!</strong><br><br><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong><br><br>- Large locations.<br>- Interesting and simple gameplay.<br>- Beautiful graphics.<br>- Unforgettable atmosphere.",
